values.Script: Dialogue(Mother Nature created us. She can destroy us too!)

Set(StillShopping, true)
While(StillShopping == true)
   Choice(Show Food Money, Buy Food($1), No Thanks)
      Case BuyFood
         If(Money > 0)
            Incr(FoodSupply, 1)
            Incr(Money, -1)
         If(Money <= 0)
            Dialogue(What do you take me for!?)
            Set(StillShopping, false)
      Case NoThanks
         Set(StillShopping, false)

Choice(Show Food Money Days, End The Day, Continue Exploring)
   Case End The Day
      DayPass(WorldMap, 99, 101)
   Case Continue Spending Time Here
      Move(Player, Up 1)

   Case End The Day
      DayPass(WorldMap, 99, 101)

values.Name: Equipment1
values.Script:
Choice(Stick [Atk + 1] $15, No Thanks)
   Case Stick [Atk + 1] $15
      If(Money < 15)
         Dialogue(You don't have enough money.)
      If(Money >= 15)
         Dialogue(You purchased the stick.)
         AddItem(Stick)
         Erase(Me)
   Case No Thanks
      Wait(0.1)

Choice(Lid [Def + 1] $15, No Thanks)
   Case Lid [Def + 1] $15
      If(Money < 15)
         Dialogue(You don't have enough money.)
      If(Money >= 15)
         Dialogue(You purchased the Lid.)
         AddItem(Lid)
         Erase(Me)
   Case No Thanks
      Wait(0.1)

Dialogue(Don't try anything fancy.)
